overview.en: Superstring theory is a powerful theory that describes nature in a single, harmonious digital framework. Adhering to this concept, Superstring Unity integrates different computing power varieties in the industry on the united platform, providing customers with one-stop aggregation mining services of full currency.Based on the experience of previous projects, the SuperstringUnity team integrated DEFI concept and launched the latest platform - SuperstringUnity mining project.
overview.zh: 超弦理论是一个能在单独的和谐数字框架下描写自然界所有力的理论。超弦聚合秉承这种理念，将业内不同算力品种整合在独创的超弦聚合平台上，为客户提供全币种一站式聚合挖矿服务。超弦聚合团队在过往项目经验的基础上，整合DEFI理念，厚积薄发，重磅推出最新平台-超弦聚合挖矿项目。
